data.meta_description: Amy Poehler is an American actress and comedian, best known for her seven years as a cast-member on Saturday Night Live
data.text:
Hitched

Poehler's husband, Will Arnett, was her co-star in 2007's Blades of Glory. The couple play a brother and sister ice-skating team that competes against the first all-male pairs skating team, played by Will Ferrell and Jon Heder.
